    h1 Single Departmental Plan
.row
  .col-sm-6
    p.lede These goals have been selected for reporting in the Single Departmental Plan.
  .col-sm-6
    == render 'goals/pie_chart_prep.html.slim'
    ==render partial: 'goals/pie_chart', locals: {goals: @goals, goal_scope: {sdp: true}}
